	@echo "⠀⠀⠈⡇⠀⡜⠀⢀⠎⢸⢸⢰⠁⠀⠄⠀⢠⠃⠀⠀⢸⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⡇⠀⠀⡆⠀⠀⣶⣿⡿⠿⡛⢻⡟⡇⠀⠀⠀⡇⠀⣿⣆⢡⠀⠀⢸⡇⠀⠀⠀"
	@echo "⠀⠀⢠⡏⠀⠉⢢⡎⠀⡇⣿⠊⠀⠀⠀⢠⡏⠀⠀⠀⠎⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⡇⠀⡸⠀⠀⠀⡇⠀⢰⡆⡇⢸⢠⢹⠀⠀⠀⡇⠀⢹⠈⢧⣣⠀⠘⡇⠀⠀⠀"
