	@echo "⢸⠁⠀⠀⢀⡠⠔⠚⠉⠉⢱⣇⢸⢧⠀⠀⠸⣱⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣀⣀⡤⠦⡔⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢀⡼⠀⠀⣼⡏⠀⠀⢹⡇⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀"
	@echo "⢸⠀⠀⠀⠋⠀⠀⠀⢀⡠⠤⣿⣾⣇⣧⠀⠀⢫⡆⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢨⠀⠀⣠⠇⠀⠀⢀⡠⣶⠋⠀⠀⡸⣾⠁⠀⠀⠈⠁⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀"
	@echo "⢸⡄⠀⠀⠀⠀⠠⠊⠁⠀⠀⢸⢃⠘⡜⡵⡀⠈⢿⡱⢲⡤⠤⢀⣀⣀⡀⠉⠉⣀⡠⡴⠚⠉⣸⢸⠀⠀⢠⣿⣿⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀"
	@echo "⠀⢧⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣀⠤⠚⠚⣤⣵⡰⡑⡄⠀⢣⡈⠳⡀⠀⠀⠀⢨⡋⠙⣆⢸⠀⠀⣰⢻⡎⠀⠀⡎⡇⡇⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀"
