	@echo "⠀⠀⢠⣿⠢⡀⠀⠀⠀⠠⠄⡖⠋⠀⠀⠙⢿⣳⡀⠑⢄⠹⣄⡀⠙⢄⡠⠤⠒⠚⡖⡇⠀⠘⣽⡇⢠⠃⢸⢀⡇⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀"
